706519f-a.title: Brooklyn: Rockaway Parkway - Conklin Avenue
706519f-a.text:
Rockaway Parkway, horth from Conklin Aven e, show-
ing a W. P. A. highway project. In the beckground is
the tower of the fire house of Engine No. 257, at Farra-
gut Road. View 2 is in the same direction from Glenwood
Road; view 3 shows the bend in the Parkway, between Farra-
gut Road and Foster Avenue. At this point Rockaway Park-
way ends and Rockaway Avenue begins.
1936
Views 1,2,3
Works Progress Administration
Five Boroughs Project
